Humility shouldn’t be a lonely experience. It should instead result in deep bonding and commitment. There’s no stronger bond than one that comes out of humility.
Make sure that the humble deed you perform had a lasting effect instead of fading away after a little while.
Today is Thirty-Four Days, which is Four Weeks and Six Days of the Omer.
Hayom shloshim u'shiva yom, she'hem shavuah echad v'shloshah yamim la'omer.